Content:: Dr Nalinda Jayatissa (born 21 April 1977) is a Sri Lankan politician and a member of the Parliament of Sri Lanka. He was elected from Kalutara District in 2015. He is a Member of the Janatha Vimukthi Peramuna.[1][2] He is a Medical Doctor.  This article about a politician from Western Province, Sri Lanka is a stub. You can help Wikipedia by expanding it.
